{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.1","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 2:1","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.001.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.002.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Pr\u00e9paratifs de Salomon pour la construction du temple<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-18: cf. 1 R 5. \u00c9s 60:13.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.2.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Salomon ordonna que l\u2019on b\u00e2t\u00eet une maison au nom de l\u2019\u00c9ternel et une maison royale pour lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2","name":"2 Chroniques 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2.2","name":"2 Chroniques 2:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1.17","name":"2 Chroniques 1:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.2","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 2:2","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.002.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.002.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.2.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Salomon compta soixante-dix mille hommes pour porter les fardeaux, quatre-vingt mille pour tailler les pierres dans la montagne, et trois mille six cents pour les surveiller.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2","name":"2 Chroniques 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2.3","name":"2 Chroniques 2:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2.1","name":"2 Chroniques 2:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.3","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 2:3","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.002.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.002.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.2.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Salomon envoya dire \u00e0 Huram, roi de Tyr: Fais pour moi comme tu as fait pour David, mon p\u00e8re, \u00e0 qui tu as envoy\u00e9 des c\u00e8dres afin qu\u2019il se b\u00e2t\u00eet une maison d\u2019habitation.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2","name":"2 Chroniques 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2.4","name":"2 Chroniques 2:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2.2","name":"2 Chroniques 2:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.4","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 2:4","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.002.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.002.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.2.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Voici, j\u2019\u00e9l\u00e8ve une maison au nom de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, mon Dieu, pour la lui consacrer, pour br\u00fbler devant lui le parfum odorif\u00e9rant, pour pr\u00e9senter continuellement les pains de proposition, et pour offrir les holocaustes du matin et du soir, des sabbats, des nouvelles lunes, et des f\u00eates de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, notre Dieu, suivant une loi perp\u00e9tuelle pour Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2","name":"2 Chroniques 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2.5","name":"2 Chroniques 2:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2.3","name":"2 Chroniques 2:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.5","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 2:5","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.002.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.002.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.2.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>La maison que je vais b\u00e2tir doit \u00eatre grande, car notre Dieu est plus grand que tous les dieux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2","name":"2 Chroniques 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2.6","name":"2 Chroniques 2:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2.4","name":"2 Chroniques 2:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.6","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 2:6","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.002.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.002.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.2.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Mais qui a le pouvoir de lui b\u00e2tir une maison, puisque les cieux et les cieux des cieux ne peuvent le contenir? Et qui suis-je pour lui b\u00e2tir une maison, si ce n\u2019est pour faire br\u00fbler des parfums devant lui?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2","name":"2 Chroniques 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2.7","name":"2 Chroniques 2:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2.5","name":"2 Chroniques 2:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.7","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 2:7","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.002.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.002.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.2.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Envoie-moi donc un homme habile pour les ouvrages en or, en argent, en airain et en fer, en \u00e9toffes teintes en pourpre, en cramoisi et en bleu, et connaissant la sculpture, afin qu\u2019il travaille avec les hommes habiles qui sont aupr\u00e8s de moi en Juda et \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem et que David, mon p\u00e8re, a choisis.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2","name":"2 Chroniques 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2.8","name":"2 Chroniques 2:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2.6","name":"2 Chroniques 2:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.8","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 2:8","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.002.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.002.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.2.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Envoie-moi aussi du Liban des bois de c\u00e8dre, de cypr\u00e8s et de sandal; car je sais que tes serviteurs s\u2019entendent \u00e0 couper les bois du Liban. Voici, mes serviteurs seront avec les tiens.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2","name":"2 Chroniques 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2.9","name":"2 Chroniques 2:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2.7","name":"2 Chroniques 2:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.9","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 2:9","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.002.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.002.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.2.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Que l\u2019on me pr\u00e9pare du bois en abondance, car la maison que je vais b\u00e2tir sera grande et magnifique.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2","name":"2 Chroniques 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2.10","name":"2 Chroniques 2:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2.8","name":"2 Chroniques 2:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.10","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 2:10","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.002.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.002.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.2.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Je donnerai \u00e0 tes serviteurs qui couperont, qui abattront les bois, vingt mille cors de froment foul\u00e9, vingt mille cors d\u2019orge, vingt mille baths de vin, et vingt mille baths d\u2019huile.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2","name":"2 Chroniques 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2.11","name":"2 Chroniques 2:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2.9","name":"2 Chroniques 2:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.11","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 2:11","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.002.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.002.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.2.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Huram, roi de Tyr, r\u00e9pondit dans une lettre qu\u2019il envoya \u00e0 Salomon: C\u2019est parce que l\u2019\u00c9ternel aime son peuple qu\u2019il t\u2019a \u00e9tabli roi sur eux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2","name":"2 Chroniques 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2.12","name":"2 Chroniques 2:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2.10","name":"2 Chroniques 2:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.12","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 2:12","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.002.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.002.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.2.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Huram dit encore: B\u00e9ni soit l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, qui a fait les cieux et la terre, de ce qu\u2019il a donn\u00e9 au roi David un fils sage, prudent et intelligent, qui va b\u00e2tir une maison \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel et une maison royale pour lui!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2","name":"2 Chroniques 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2.13","name":"2 Chroniques 2:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2.11","name":"2 Chroniques 2:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.13","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 2:13","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.002.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.002.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.2.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Je t\u2019envoie donc un homme habile et intelligent,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2","name":"2 Chroniques 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2.14","name":"2 Chroniques 2:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2.12","name":"2 Chroniques 2:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.14","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 2:14","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.002.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.002.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.2.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Huram-Abi, fils d\u2019une femme d\u2019entre les filles de Dan, et d\u2019un p\u00e8re Tyrien. Il est habile pour les ouvrages en or, en argent, en airain et en fer, en pierre et en bois, en \u00e9toffes teintes en pourpre et en bleu, en \u00e9toffes de byssus et de carmin, et pour toute esp\u00e8ce de sculptures et d\u2019objets d\u2019art qu\u2019on lui donne \u00e0 ex\u00e9cuter. Il travaillera avec tes hommes habiles et avec les hommes habiles de mon seigneur David, ton p\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2","name":"2 Chroniques 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2.15","name":"2 Chroniques 2:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2.13","name":"2 Chroniques 2:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.15","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 2:15","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.002.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.002.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.2.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Maintenant, que mon seigneur envoie \u00e0 ses serviteurs le froment, l\u2019orge, l\u2019huile et le vin dont il a parl\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2","name":"2 Chroniques 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2.16","name":"2 Chroniques 2:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2.14","name":"2 Chroniques 2:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.16","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 2:16","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.002.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.002.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.2.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Et nous, nous couperons des bois du Liban autant que tu en auras besoin; nous te les exp\u00e9dierons par mer en radeaux jusqu\u2019\u00e0 Japho, et tu les feras monter \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2","name":"2 Chroniques 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2.17","name":"2 Chroniques 2:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2.15","name":"2 Chroniques 2:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.17","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 2:17","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.002.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.002.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.2.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Salomon compta tous les \u00e9trangers qui \u00e9taient dans le pays d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, et dont le d\u00e9nombrement avait \u00e9t\u00e9 fait par David, son p\u00e8re. On en trouva cent cinquante-trois mille six cents.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2","name":"2 Chroniques 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2.18","name":"2 Chroniques 2:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2.16","name":"2 Chroniques 2:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.18","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 2:18","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.002.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.003.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.2.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Et il en prit soixante-dix mille pour porter les fardeaux, quatre-vingt mille pour tailler les pierres dans la montagne, et trois mille six cents pour surveiller et faire travailler le peuple.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2","name":"2 Chroniques 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3.1","name":"2 Chroniques 3:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2.17","name":"2 Chroniques 2:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb3cbd3a2.12372903');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb3cbd3a2.12372903\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb3cbd3a2.12372903","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb3cbd3a2.12372903'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb3cbd3a2.12372903\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}